==Dutch==
===Noun===
'''beeld''' {{n}} (''plural:'' '''beelden''')
#Two-dimensional visual representation of something.
#:''Het '''beeld''' van deze televisie is heel slecht.'' - ''This television's image is very bad.''
#Artistic representation of something using solid materials such as marble, hardened clay or metal.
#The idea one has of something.
#:''Het '''beeld''' dat je van hem hebt, klopt niet.'' - ''The impresssion you have of him is incorrect.''

